STATE of Louisiana
v.
Francis WINCHESTER NO. 2018-KH-1804 Supreme Court of Louisiana. May 20, 2019 Denied. Applicant has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See State ex rel. Winchester v. State, 18-0005 (La. 11/05/18), 255 So.3d 1037 . WEIMER, J., recused.
